{"commentv2": 1, "number": 36, "id": 223135, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "hordegecko", "body": "In theory it is possible to one man Gruul, since all the damage he does is physical anyone with 100% avoidance can theoretically solo him. The hardest part of it would be avoiding the cave ins.", "date": "2008-01-23T23:52:52-06:00", "rating": 4, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 37, "id": 227929, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "88528", "body": "Even if you're bubbled, \"Shatter\" will STILL do damage to you", "date": "2008-02-01T16:27:18-06:00", "rating": 16, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Same with iceblock", "creationdate": "2008-03-14T11:46:51-05:00", "id": 28238, "rating": 10, "commentid": 227929, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "108239", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "The same goes for Cloak of Shadows, although you can still move freely.", "creationdate": "2008-06-01T19:21:35-05:00", "id": 35234, "rating": 0, "commentid": 227929, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "NinjaPirate", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 38, "id": 236064, "nreplies": 7, "sticky": 0, "user": "128172", "body": "Is it possible to taunt Gruul, because i was doing this fight with my guild and our MT died. I was the only other tank alive and i was last in threat with maybe 50k threat, and the other tank that was alive had 300k threat, within a couple seconds i got myself to the top of the threat list.\r\n\r\nI wanna make sure i know whether or not it was the taunt that gave me 250k threat or if it was my leet tanking", "date": "2008-02-14T14:03:05-06:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Gruul is immune to taunt. There is one explanation I can think of what happened, though: It could be that everyone in threat above you was killed, and so you'd be top in threat eventually.", "creationdate": "2008-02-28T07:56:21-06:00", "id": 27025, "rating": 7, "commentid": 236064, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "102270", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "As much as it says \"immune\" when you taunt him, it's possible he may be immune to the redirection of his focus and you probably still got a copy of the highest threat.  Just because something says \"immune\" doesn't mean it's immune to every effect that is a part of that skill.  imo, you shouldn't of been modded down, but the crowd that is wowhead is a tough one ;) - this is also worth looking into for the sake of threat meters.", "creationdate": "2008-03-03T12:31:21-06:00", "id": 27345, "rating": 5, "commentid": 236064, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "thantik", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Just want to confirm.  I've been OT for the Gruul kill for the past few weeks and Taunt does \"work\" on Gruul.  When the OT taunts, his threat will jump up and match that of the Main Tank, although Gruul's focus will not change.  This makes OTing Gruul a simple matter of Taunting and keeping TC, Demo, and CS/BS up.  Use whatever damaging moves you want in order to burn up your rage, most likely SB/Revange and SS/HS.", "creationdate": "2008-06-04T07:08:32-05:00", "id": 337106, "rating": 1, "commentid": 236064, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Porcell", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "There is a well known flaw in Omen where if a mob is immune to taunts, Omen will still show the \"threat\" gained by the taunt despite the immunity  Gruul is completely immune to taunt", "creationdate": "2008-07-07T15:39:25-05:00", "id": 38853, "rating": 3, "commentid": 236064, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "ir0npanda", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "lol @ the person who said that 250k threat could be caused by misdirect.  I wish that my misdirect would give the tank 250k threat, but that could not occur.  Hunters do not have any abilites that could come even CLOSE to that kind of threat.  Maximum a hunter could probably pull off would be 10k threat if they were really good.", "creationdate": "2008-07-10T00:55:40-05:00", "id": 341037, "rating": 1, "commentid": 236064, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "ericslash", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
