{"commentv2": 1, "number": 74, "id": 1362170, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "citrique", "body": "Gruul is a mindless tank and spank for any melee soloing him at 85. If you're doing it as a tank class, leave 2-3 of the Lair Brute trash alive when you pull him, them hitting you will generate vengeance so he dies faster. For a DK at least, it's near-impossible to go below 80% health even with 3 adds hitting you in the back while you kill him.\r\n\r\nJust remember not to kill him right after a Ground Slam, until he does Shatter - otherwise you'll sit stunned for 30 seconds after he dies and if adds are alive, they will kill you.", "date": "2011-03-09T10:16:01-06:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 75, "id": 1377113, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Nepipen", "body": "Duoed for the second time today.\r\n125g loot per boss -- Gruul and his %^&*! minions\r\n+ the loot from bosses = win :D\r\n\r\nFirst Boss:\r\nFrost Mage\r\nHoly Pally\r\n\r\nGruul:\r\nFrost Mage\r\nProt Pally\r\n\r\n\r\nSTRAT:\r\nOn the first boss, the frost mage (Fuqq--Stormscale) dps'd the seer down (must silence all the time) and killed him then killed the lock then it's all down hill.\r\nThe entire fight, I healed just running around being feared and holy shocking/word of glorying as I could and held aggro on every boss except the boss Fuqq was killing. (Had to LOH and bubble and all the works.)\r\n\r\nI flipped prot for Gruul-- seems to be easier/faster-- just a simple tank and spank fight, easy as it was then only takes longer. Stay outta #$%^ that falls\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[quote][/quote] Guess we found out this guy's weakness... bullets.", "date": "2011-03-27T00:18:10-05:00", "rating": -2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
