{"commentv2": 1, "number": 81, "id": 1648227, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "naihtsirc", "body": "Solo'd as frost mage (~380 ilvl), popped all cd's at start (mirror image, time warp, trinkets). If you go invisible before the mirror images run out you'll reset your aggro which gives some breathing room to evocate/bandage. Make sure your water elemental keeps attacking (and is not invisible) though otherwise the boss will reset when the mirror images expire.", "date": "2012-04-03T08:55:03-05:00", "rating": -3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
