{"commentv2": 1, "number": 85, "id": 1686211, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Balla0529", "body": "Marksmanship (7/31/3) Hunter.\r\nBallinhunts, of Kargath-US.\r\n409 iLvl\r\n\r\nUsing a turtle as the \"Go-To\" [b]tenacity[/b] pet, I find it easy to solo (duo really) all of the old content as an appropriately-spec'ed [b]Marksmanship[/b] Hunter.\r\n\r\nI advise the use of [b]Glyph of Mending[/b] and [b]Glyph of Misdirection[/b] as two critical Major Glyphs, the other choices are yours to make.\r\n\r\nAs has been previously mentioned, [i]Gruul the Dragonkiller[/i] is indeed a pushover compared to [i]High King Maulgar[/i].\r\n\r\nSimply Misdirect your (tenacity) pet, and win (while making sure you're occasionally misdirecting your pet for aggro purposes). [u]Just make sure to move out of the Cave-Ins![/u]\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions, feel free to contact me in-game!", "date": "2012-07-09T02:32:22-05:00", "rating": -2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
